entry.name: linkedin-learning
entry.description: LinkedIn Learning (formerly lynda.com) is an American massive open online course website offering video courses taught by industry experts in software, creative, and business skills. It is a subsidiary of LinkedIn.

entry.name: linkedin-learning-downloading
entry.description: This App-ID identifies the downloading activity of Linkedin Learning, including assignment download and notes export except Course Video downloading (caching).

entry.name: linkedin-learning-editing
entry.description: This App-ID identifies the editing activity of Linkedin Learning, including modifying course notes, changing interested skill set, changing course status, and adding/removing bookmarks on courses.

entry.name: linkedin-learning-posting
entry.description: This App-ID identifies the posting activity of Linkedin Learning, including posting questions in Q&A section, posting course notes, and posting feedback to courses.

entry.name: linkedin-learning-video
entry.description: This App-ID identifies the video streaming activity of Linkedin Learning ,including online watching and course video downloading (pre-caching).
